# Errors, toasts, and notifications

## Canonical sources (no separate doc files)

| Concern | Where |
|---------|--------|
| Sonner toasts, `showError` / `showSuccess`, `errors.*` keys | `src/lib/error-handler.ts`; translation keys in `messages/en.json` & `messages/ar.json` |
| `notify*`, email, in-app, WhatsApp, **`locale`** from `ctx` | `src/lib/notifications/`; context locale from `src/server/trpc.ts` |
| Channels and subscription cron (business framing) | `docs/ADVANCED_BUSINESS.md` |
| SSE/cron path pointers | `docs/ADVANCED_TECHNICAL.md` |

## Agent checklist

- **Client toasts**: `useTranslations()` → pass `t` as third arg to `showError`, `showSuccess`, `showWarning`, `showInfo` in `@/lib/error-handler`.
- **Server notifications**: pass **`locale`** (e.g. `ctx.locale`) into notification helpers under `@/lib/notifications/`.
- **Single source of truth**: extend shared helpers and translation JSON — avoid one-off translated strings in random components.
